    "uen": "201627452Z",
    "description": "<p><strong>ABA EduArt Pte Ltd</strong>is one of the top leading D.I.Y education program service organization in Taiwan, Singapore and Mainland China. We started this journey in 2016 where we reached out to elite Primary and Secondary Schools. The unique kinaesthetic learning programs at ABA EduArt is modelled after our successful franchise in Taiwan, and Mainland China.</p>\n<p>In Singapore, we aim to deliver flexible and scalable D.I.Y programs designed to help students to improve their creativity, hands-on abilities, and build up “<strong>Craftsman Spirit</strong>”. Most importantly, it satisfy our MOE’s vision for S.T.E.M education. The program created at <strong>ABA EduArt </strong>makes learning fun, engaging and experiential and we aim to cater specifically to all MOE schools in Singapore.</p>\n<p><strong>ABA EduArt </strong>seeks to attract highly motivated individuals who has interest in the education business, able to work as a team and shares our vision. We want to attract disciplined individuals who are comfortable meeting aggressive goals and expectations. Their success will in turn enable <strong>ABA EduArt </strong>to give its employees above average compensation and innovative benefits, key elements in helping us maintain our leadership position in the marketplace.</p>\n<p>If you wish to join a fast-growing company that takes an innovative and meaningful approach to education, send in your resume now!</p>",
